of early adopters that were really into

27
00:01:38.619 --> 00:01:43.079
the service, but they had some
really big growth problems, right?

28
00:01:43.079 --> 00:01:46.402
Their servers would go down a lot,
people would complain about it.

29
00:01:46.402 --> 00:01:48.682
And then the unthinkable happened,

30
00:01:48.682 --> 00:01:52.442
