number of people's photographs.

31
00:01:52.442 --> 00:01:55.342
You can't get much worse than that, right?

32
00:01:55.342 --> 00:02:01.105
So what Flickr did is instead
of releasing a legal statement

33
00:02:01.105 --> 00:02:06.060
