they wrote a post saying

34
00:02:06.060 --> 00:02:11.489
sometimes we suck, right,
and they just apologized.

35
00:02:11.489 --> 00:02:14.113
They apologized,
they said what went wrong,

36
00:02:14.113 --> 00:02:18.703
they said how they were gonna fix it, and
they said how they compensated people.

37
00:02:18.703 --> 00:02:25.057
No trying to wiggle out of it,
no corporate BS, nothing like that,

38
00:02:25.057 --> 00:02:30.522
they just were honest and
open and human and transparent.

39
00:02:30.522 --> 00:02:36.298
And that paid off hugely for them,
they turned those early adopters into

40
00:02:36.298 --> 00:02:41.895
advocates with their attitude and
their approach and their honesty.

41
00:02:41.895 --> 00:02:47.702
And so often we fail to do this
basic thing on our websites,

42
00:02:47.702 --> 00:02:53.638
